{
  "stem": "7094.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember very much there was a teacher that his wife taught me from my childhood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when he-- when the Russian came in, he-- because he was a nationalist, he didn't have a job under Poland.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then he became-- he had a job and he was a mathematician.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was very proud of me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Every exhibition, every visit used to show off with me how-- how good his teaching was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "During the war, he didn't recognize me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He just walked-- somebody who knew me from childhood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "His wife used to always invite me because she was very proud of my achievement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He was very-- This is-- there was a change completely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in the offices, you know, some of my school friends would sit behind the office and command me, doing it again and again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was a kind of humiliation part.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and the Judenrat, this is a subject on its own, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It's very controversial.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The people blame a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I understand how it happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We always had a Judenrat you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The community always had a-- a Judenrat, which were the elders of the town who-- During the German, they didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They elected.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My father refused to be elected to that committee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But a lot of people went into it, with quite innocently trying-- it needed organizing, because the German would come in and demand.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "If an administrator came in, we had to give up our furniture or anything what they demanded to give, so you need to have a go-between.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they started in an innocent way to be the-- the go-between, to-- to represent the community before the German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, some of them have became corrupt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's understandable.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
